criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Six preschools with the following criteria:

          -  located in Harlem, NY;

          -  public school;

          -  children 3, 4 and 5 years of age;

          -  availability of the use of the cafeteria.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Participation in any other major structured health intervention program similar to the
             FAMILIA Program during the evaluation of the program

          -  Inability to carry out all activities proposed by the FAMILIA Program
